 в•ҡв•җв•җв•җв•§в•җв•җв•җв•§в•җв•җв•җв•қ
                </pre>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card-header">Tic-Tac-Toe</div>
            <p class="project-card-desc">Classic 3-in-a-row. Play against an unbeatable AI using the Minimax algorithm.</p>
